Gcina ibhethri yakho iphilile isikhathi eside ngokuba nengemuva elimnyama
Izinyathelo ezingeziwe zibandakanya umsizi we-Google, i-Google Pay, Okudlala Manje, usayizi wefonti, isithombe sangemuva, nokuningi
Qhubeka ukuze wenze ifoni yengane yakho isethwe ngokugcwele. Noma, hamba manje uphinde uthole isikhumbuzo sokuqedelela emuva kwesikhathi.

Ithatha isikhathi eside kakhulu? Zama ukubuyela emuva uphinde uxhumeke kunethiwekhi ehlukile.
Imigmo yesevisi kanye nenqubomgomo yobumfihlo ye-Google iyasebenza. Ngemininingwane engeziwe, vakashela ku-www.google.com/policies.
Buza umlawuli wakho we-IT ukuze uthole ikhodi elungile
I-iPhone, i-iPad, i-iOS, i-iMessage, i-iCloud, i-Safari ne-iTunes izimpawu zokuhweba ze-Apple Inc., ezibhaliswe e-U.S. nakwamanye amazwe.
Ukuze uthole ama-app nokuningi, xhumeka kunethiwekhi ye-Wi-Fi noma sebenzisa idatha yeselula
Ukuze ulande i-SIM yakho, xhuma ku-Wi‑Fi
Zama futhi usebenzisa enye inethiwekhi. Uma uqhubeka ngaphandle kokuxhumeka, ungaqedela ezinye izinyathelo zokusetha ngemuva kwesikhathi.

Ngokuqhubeka uphinde uthole lesi sibuyekezo sesofthiwe, uvumela Imigomo Yesevisi ye-Google kanye nokuthi Inqubomgomo Yemfihlo.
